title: I Forgot That You Existed
description:
Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey are excited to deep dive into an album that Taylor owns while we anxiously await for her next re-release.. Welcome to the Lover era!
We kick it off with a genius Track 1 from Taylor.. I Forgot That You Existed! Who all is this bop about? And how does the 5 holes theory tie into this song?
What did we miss? What would you like to hear? Let us know!
